'''The Long Now Foundation''' wants to promote thinking about the extremely long term, and have to the project to build a clock that only ticks every 10,000 years.

Their seminars are fascinating thoughts about the long term future of humanity. 

URL = http://seminars.moose.cc/

Amongst the speakers are Brian Eno, Peter Schwartz, George Dyson, Bruce Sterling, etc..

President and initiator of the Long Now Foundation, '''Stewart Brand''', is interviewed here at http://www.massivechange.com/interviews.html. Transcript available here at
http://www.massivechange.com/StewartBrand.html

